      • calculateParts

        public static LinkedList<Part> calculateParts(Carport carport,
                                              LinkedList<Part> boM)
        This initialises the different methods for calculating the smaller parts of the Bill of Materials (BoM). Utilizes the part constructor when creating parts. Utilizes the BoM generated by WoodCalc as many of the parts are needed for the calculations.
        Parameters:
        carport - carport with length, width, shed or no shed, type of roof and height.
        boM - the part list for the wood. Needed for the calculations with relation to screws and fittings.
        Returns:
        LinkedList with Parts
